name: intelligent-transportation-systems-research-data-exchange-minnesota-dot-mobile-observation-ec672
notes: Registered users can download the RDE API client application and receive a real-time data feed from the Minnesota Integrated Mobile Observation (IMO) project. Mobile (vehicle based) observations of road weather related and other data is provided from Minnesota DOT maintenance vehicles in this FHWA sponsored project. This data is also saved as archive files.
